  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "No tickets at Colombo Fort Railway Station",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The OICs will not be called to work at the Colombo Fort Railway Station until the railway authorities provide the correct information regarding the delayed trains and the canceled trains.",
        "Mr. Chamara said that the OIC had been evacuated yesterday afternoon for the safety of the people during the riots at the railway station and that in order to return to work, the public should be able to provide information when asked.",
        "Mr. Kasun Chamara said that even though the authorities told the media that the train was running normally, it was not normal."
      ],
